lead_paragraph: The plane that crashed in Colombia virtually wiping out an entire Brazilian soccer team was running out of fuel, had no electrical power, and was preparing for an emergency landing, according to the pilot's final words.

headline.print_headline: Soccer Plane in Colombia Crash Was Running Out of Fuel: Recording
